body_preview ## HFHE v2 Cryptanalysis — Exhaustive Attack Report  **Status: UNDEFEATED — No path to plaintext recovery found with current public techniques.**  ### Summary  40+ attack tests across every known category. Found & fixed critical S-box CNF bug. All LPN approaches hit 50% wall. Independent smoke-ui assessment also negative. Deep math research confirms no exploitable structure.  ### LPN(4096, 1/8) — 15+ approaches, ALL negative  GE, bit-flipping, majority vote, correlation, SA, BKW, BKZ, SAT, XL, I
